               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440304-name-645" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18440304-name-645" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440304-name-645" type="surname" value="KING"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440304-name-645" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS KING</persName>
                  </hi>. About five o'clock on the 28th of Feb. I was passing the Strand—I turned my head and missed my silk handkerchief—I had seen it safe five minutes before—the prisoner was behind me—I watched him—I af<lb></lb>terwards told a policeman—he stopped him, and produced my handkerchief from the prisoner's pocket.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
