                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable H</hi> 37.) I stopped the prisoner—the prosecutor said he had got his handkerchief—I asked the prisoner if he had it—he said no—I asked him again, and he produced these two handkerchiefs—one is the prosecutor's; the other has "J. H." on it.</p>
               <p>
